{"tid":1418242,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"警黑合作，既然政府唔會重組警隊。。","createTime":"2019-08-05T18:10:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T18:11:32.000Z","uid":269304,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f17a7b201e83b5d69d86affe88ecb4243ce0b81b","tid":1418242,"uid":269304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:10:40.000Z","msg":"致<br />\n不再相信政府和克警的手足：<br />\n反對立法會即將通過警察加薪的手足：<br />\n對於JUPUS放榜覺得徬徨的手足：<br />\n<br />\n警黑合作，無法無天！有良心的人才已逐漸留失，包括轉至相關行業例如保安系統顧問，學堂退學情況嚴重等等。餘下只有走狗（媚共），機械人（只執行任務），社會底層（沒能力轉工）的人<br />\n<br />\n我地應該用自己的方法建立屬於香港人的警隊<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家一齊考警察！</span></span>"},{"pid":"c48fb5e26b0e1358babda2fa924f3ad0f37f68f4","tid":1418242,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:10:50.000Z","msg":"前線只接受禮貌啲叫人唔好影相呢個point<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1417999\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1417999</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5136cf739bb9f45f3d646646e42dd40cedce39f5","tid":1418242,"uid":271413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:11:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}